<TITLE> Iraq's Sadr threatens to lift ceasefire </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Bagdad, April 8 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Iraqi cleric Moqtada al-Sadr threatened on Tuesday to lift a ceasefire he imposed his Mehdi Army militia last August. "If it is required to lift the freeze (ceasefire) in order to carry out our goals, objectives, doctrines and religious principles and patriotism, we will do that later and in a separate statement," Sadr said in a statement published on his Web site
